    "description": "<strong>这是 Crack it Up! 的免费序章版本！<br>在此版本中，你可以完成你的第一个收藏并体验游戏的主要机制。<br>别忘了将完整游戏加入你的愿望清单，以便在游戏发布时收到通知！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/87d1ee7c06f64dc82db7dd3b7d6bb3f4.avif?t=1729062778\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >购买卡包</h2>使用你的电脑从网上商店订购不同类型的卡包。在这个轻松的卡片收藏游戏中，一个接一个地打开卡包。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.poster.avif?t=1729062778\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.webm?t=1729062778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/8f0dcb3c3590e698dd1d2943f50c23a3.mp4?t=1729062778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 购买不同收藏系列的卡包。<br></li><li> 优质卡包，有高概率获得独特的稀有卡。<br></li><li> 大量卡包的卡盒，更划算。<br></li><li> 轻松的开卡包玩法。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/712f51fee1c3dd8cb2c5ce8982295231.avif?t=1729062778\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >出售卡片</h2>作为一个狂热的卡片收藏家，你最终会有大量的卡片收藏。在一个网页上出售你的重复卡和最稀有的卡以获取利润。管理你的经济，并在不断变化的卡片交易市场中获得最佳交易。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/69cfdc7a6136d549f16a1e6836281127.poster.avif?t=1729062778\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/69cfdc7a6136d549f16a1e6836281127.webm?t=1729062778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/69cfdc7a6136d549f16a1e6836281127.mp4?t=1729062778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 使用你的复古电脑在网上商店出售卡片。<br></li><li> 动态的卡片市场，卡片价格随时间变化。选择合适的时机出售，以最大化你的利润。<br></li><li> 管理你的经济，你会卖掉那张稀有的卡片赚大钱，还是把它保留在你的收藏中？</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/2e2820ef4688daa17a2f6563254a3e94.avif?t=1729062778\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完成收藏</h2>作为一个卡片收藏爱好者，你将有不同的收藏可以完成，每个收藏都有数百张卡片和高价值的稀有变体。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/bf986be2d6b8c6d1ba728efb3a1b423e.poster.avif?t=1729062778\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/bf986be2d6b8c6d1ba728efb3a1b423e.webm?t=1729062778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017090/extras/bf986be2d6b8c6d1ba728efb3a1b423e.mp4?t=1729062778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 完成多达5个不同的卡片收藏。<br></li><li> 数百张带有稀有变体的卡片。<br></li><li> 浏览你的收藏册，检查你珍贵的交易卡片。</li></ul>",
